      "role": "user",
      "content": "depersonalization... i don't know. it just feels more permanent than a symptom. like the real person actually died and this is just the ghost left behind. its exhausting trying to pretend to be a human when i feel like zero. what's even the point of keeping up the act if there's nobody actually home?",
