    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so fake though. every day is just a script. i'm just going through the motions, smiling when i'm supposed to, talking when i'm supposed to... but there's nothing inside. it feels like i'm just wasting a lot of time being a hollow copy of a person. it would be so much quieter if the movie just stopped.",
